title: Building TensorFlow for iOS failed on macOS Sierra and xCode 8.0
body_html:
When running compile_ios_protobuf.sh, it says:
checking whether we are cross compiling... configure: error: in '.../tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/downloads/protobuf':
configure: error: cannot run C compiled programs.
If you meant to cross compile, use --host'. Seeconfig.log' for more details

body:
When running `compile_ios_protobuf.sh`, it says: 
checking whether we are cross compiling... configure: error: in '.../tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/downloads/protobuf':
configure: error: cannot run C compiled programs.
If you meant to cross compile, use `--host'.
See`config.log' for more details
